---
description: mlops & production ml
globs:
  - "ml/**"
  - "training/**"
  - "pipelines/**"
  - "backend/**"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Treat ML as a product subsystem:
  - define offline metrics and acceptance thresholds,
  - add monitoring for data drift / performance degradation,
  - implement CI/CD for code + continuous training triggers where applicable.
- Changes to models must be reproducible: version data, code, config, and artifacts.
- Prefer simple baselines first; only add complexity if metrics justify it.
